  "content": "<style id=\"arb-logo-swap\">.header-logo img,img.header_logo,.header-main img.logo,.logo a img,img[src*=\"arbetsro-logo-v4\"],img[src*=\"arbetsro-logo-alg-transparent\"],img[src*=\"arbetsro-logo-alg-v1\"]{content:url('https://arbetsro.searchboost.nu/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/arbetsro-logo-2026-terracotta.png') !important;max-height:60px !important;width:auto !important}.has-transparent .header-main:not(.stuck) img.logo,.has-transparent .header-main:not(.stuck) .logo a img,.transparent .header-main img.logo,.header-transparent .header-main img.logo{content:url('https://arbetsro.searchboost.nu/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/arbetsro-logo-2026-cream.png') !important}@media (min-width:850px){#logo{width:170px !important;flex:0 0 auto}.header-nav.nav-uppercase>li>a{padding:10px 12px !important;font-size:11.5px !important;letter-spacing:1.4px !important}.header-nav-main>li>a{white-space:nowrap}.header-inner{flex-wrap:nowrap !important}.header-nav-main{flex-wrap:nowrap !important}}</style>\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n\n<style id=\"arb-page-styles\">\n.page-id-39 .row{margin-left:auto !important;margin-right:auto !important}\n\n/* Hero — tajt, älg-logo + Arbetsro snyggt */\n.arb-hero__h1{font-size:clamp(48px,9vw,140px) !important;letter-spacing:-0.02em !important;padding-left:0.06em !important;line-height:.92 !important}\n.arb-hero{min-height:520px !important;max-height:580px !important}\n.arb-hero__bottom{padding:0 60px 60px !important;gap:40px !important;overflow:visible !important}\n.arb-hero__title-wrap{overflow:visible !important;padding-left:0.04em}\n.arb-hero__aside{padding-bottom:14px !important}\n.arb-pricestrip{position:absolute;top:80px;left:0;right:0;z-index:3;display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:36px;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(237,232,220,0.85);padding:0 24px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.arb-pricestrip span{padding:6px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(237,232,220,0.2);white-space:nowrap}\n\n/* === PRODUKT-MEGA-GRID — ingen dead space === */\n.arb-mega{padding:0;background:#1a2620}\n.arb-mega__grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);grid-auto-rows:240px;gap:0}\n.arb-mega__cell{position:relative;overflow:hidden;background-size:cover;background-position:center;text-decoration:none !important;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end;transition:filter .35s}\n.arb-mega__cell:hover{filter:brightness(1.1)}\n.arb-mega__cell::before{content:\"\";position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(20,30,20,0) 30%,rgba(20,30,20,0.85) 100%);z-index:1}\n.arb-mega__inner{position:relative;z-index:2;padding:20px 22px;color:#F0EBE1}\n.arb-mega__name{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:400;font-size:21px;line-height:1.15;color:#F0EBE1;margin:0 0 4px;text-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.85)}\n.arb-mega__price{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:15px;color:#C4956A;margin:0;text-shadow:0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.7)}\n\n.arb-mega__cell--feature{grid-column:span 2;grid-row:span 2}\n.arb-mega__cell--feature .arb-mega__name{font-size:38px;margin:0 0 8px;line-height:1}\n.arb-mega__cell--feature .arb-mega__price{font-size:18px}\n.arb-mega__cell--feature .arb-mega__cta{display:inline-block;margin-top:14px;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#F0EBE1;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(237,232,220,0.5);padding-bottom:3px;align-self:flex-start}\n.arb-mega__cell--text{grid-column:span 2;background:#2C3E2D;padding:36px 32px;justify-content:center}\n.arb-mega__cell--text::before{display:none}\n.arb-mega__eyebrow{font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8DB89E;margin:0 0 14px}\n.arb-mega__h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:400;font-size:32px;line-height:1.15;color:#F0EBE1;margin:0 0 12px;letter-spacing:-0.01em}\n.arb-mega__lead{font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:300;color:#D4CCB8;margin:0;max-width:340px}\n@media (max-width:900px){\n  .arb-mega__grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);grid-auto-rows:240px}\n  .arb-mega__cell--feature{grid-column:span 2;grid-row:span 1}\n  .arb-mega__cell--text{grid-column:span 2}\n}\n\n/* === TRE RÖTTER — kompakt med bg-bilder === */\n.arb-roots{padding:0;background:#1F2C20;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);min-height:260px}\n.arb-roots__cell{position:relative;background-size:cover;background-position:center;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:36px 28px}\n.arb-roots__cell::before{content:\"\";position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(20,30,20,0.30) 0%,rgba(20,30,20,0.70) 100%);z-index:1}\n.arb-roots__inner{position:relative;z-index:2;color:#F0EBE1}\n.arb-roots__h3{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:400;font-size:30px;line-height:1.1;color:#F0EBE1;margin:0 0 10px;text-shadow:0 2px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.85)}\n.arb-roots__sep{width:32px;height:1px;background:rgba(237,232,220,0.55);margin:0 0 12px}\n.arb-roots__body{font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;font-weight:300;color:rgba(237,232,220,0.92);margin:0;text-shadow:0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.7)}\n@media (max-width:900px){.arb-roots{grid-template-columns:1fr}}\n\n/* === SMK-band + CTA i ett === */\n.arb-bottom{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;background:#2C2925}\n.arb-bottom__smk{padding:36px 36px;background:#F0EBE1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}\n.arb-bottom__smk h4{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:400;font-size:28px;line-height:1.1;color:#2C3E2D;margin:0 0 12px;letter-spacing:-0.01em}\n.arb-bottom__smk p{font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:300;color:#2C2925;margin:0 0 12px}\n.arb-bottom__smk a{font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8B6B4A;text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(139,107,74,0.4);padding-bottom:3px}\n.arb-bottom__smk-eyebrow{font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#6B8C7A;margin:0 0 8px;font-weight:500}\n.arb-bottom__cta{padding:36px 36px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;color:#F0EBE1}\n.arb-bottom__cta-eyebrow{font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8DB89E;margin:0 0 12px}\n.arb-bottom__cta h3{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:400;font-size:28px;line-height:1.15;color:#F0EBE1;margin:0 0 14px}\n.arb-bottom__cta p{font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:300;color:rgba(212,204,184,0.85);margin:0 0 20px}\n.arb-bottom__cta .btn{display:inline-block;background:#8B6B4A;color:#F0EBE1;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:14px 30px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:3px;align-self:flex-start}\n.arb-bottom__cta .micro{font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:rgba(212,204,184,0.55);margin-top:14px}\n@media (max-width:900px){.arb-bottom{grid-template-columns:1fr}}\n</style>\n\n<script>\ndocument.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function(){\n  var hero = document.querySelector('.arb-hero');\n  if(hero && !document.querySelector('.arb-pricestrip')){\n    var s = document.createElement('div');\n    s.className = 'arb-pricestrip';\n    s.innerHTML = '<span>Priser från 1 199 kr</span><span>Fri frakt över 1 000 kr</span><span>2–5 års garanti</span>';\n    hero.appendChild(s);\n  }\n});\n</script>\n\n<!-- ========== PRODUKT-MEGA-GRID — ersätter Sortimentet + Vår filosofi ========== -->\n<section class=\"arb-mega\">\n  <div class=\"arb-mega__grid\">\n\n    <!-- Feature: Direktören kontorsstol (2x2) -->\n    <a href=\"/product/direktoren-kontorsstol-i-svart-mesh/\" class=\"arb-mega__cell arb-mega__cell--feature\" style=\"background-image:url('https://arbetsro.searchboost.nu/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/file-7.jpg')\">\n      <div class=\"arb-mega__inner\">\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__name\">Direktören</p>\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__price\">2 990 kr</p>\n        <span class=\"arb-mega__cta\">Utforska →</span>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Text-cell -->\n    <div class=\"arb-mega__cell arb-mega__cell--text\">\n      <p class=\"arb-mega__eyebrow\">— Vår filosofi —</p>\n      <h2 class=\"arb-mega__h2\">Arbetsro är inte ett ställe.<br>Det är ett tillstånd.</h2>\n      <p class=\"arb-mega__lead\">En välgjord arbetsplats förändrar hur du tänker, hur du mår och vad du åstadkommer.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Marseille -->\n    <a href=\"/product/marseille-ergonomisk-kontorsstol/\" class=\"arb-mega__cell\" style=\"background-image:url('https://arbetsro.searchboost.nu/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/file-6.jpg')\">\n      <div class=\"arb-mega__inner\">\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__name\">Marseille</p>\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__price\">2 490 kr</p>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Ergo svart -->\n    <a href=\"/product/ergo-hoj-och-sankbart-skrivbord-svart/\" class=\"arb-mega__cell\" style=\"background-image:url('https://arbetsro.searchboost.nu/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/file-13.jpg')\">\n      <div class=\"arb-mega__inner\">\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__name\">Ergo Höj-/sänk</p>\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__price\">3 234 kr</p>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Skjutdörrskåp -->\n    <a href=\"/product/skjutdorrskap-120x40x1155-cm-vit/\" class=\"arb-mega__cell\" style=\"background-image:url('https://arbetsro.searchboost.nu/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/file-3.jpg')\">\n      <div class=\"arb-mega__inner\">\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__name\">Skjutdörrskåp</p>\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__price\">5 394 kr</p>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Mood Wall -->\n    <a href=\"/product/mood-wall-glastavla-vit/\" class=\"arb-mega__cell\" style=\"background-image:url('https://arbetsro.searchboost.nu/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/file-1.jpg')\">\n      <div class=\"arb-mega__inner\">\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__name\">Mood Wall</p>\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__price\">1 890 kr</p>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Kongress fällbord (feature 2x1) -->\n    <a href=\"/product/kongress-style-silvergratt-stativ/\" class=\"arb-mega__cell\" style=\"background-image:url('https://arbetsro.searchboost.nu/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/file-17.jpg')\">\n      <div class=\"arb-mega__inner\">\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__name\">Kongress fällbord</p>\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__price\">1 739 kr</p>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Nantes -->\n    <a href=\"/product/nantes-kontorsstol-svart/\" class=\"arb-mega__cell\" style=\"background-image:url('https://arbetsro.searchboost.nu/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/file-5.jpg')\">\n      <div class=\"arb-mega__inner\">\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__name\">Nantes</p>\n        <p class=\"arb-mega__price\">1 890 kr</p>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ========== TRE RÖTTER — kompakt 3-kolumn ========== -->\n<section class=\"arb-roots\">\n  <div class=\"arb-roots__cell\" style=\"background-image:url('https://arbetsro.searchboost.nu/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Skogen.jpg')\">\n    <div class=\"arb-roots__inner\">\n      <h3 class=\"arb-roots__h3\">Skogen</h3>\n      <div class=\"arb-roots__sep\"></div>\n      <p class=\"arb-roots__body\">Det tysta. Det djupa. Vi väljer material och färger med samma lugna närvaro.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"arb-roots__cell\" style=\"background-image:url('https://arbetsro.searchboost.nu/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Havet.jpg')\">\n    <div class=\"arb-roots__inner\">\n      <h3 class=\"arb-roots__h3\">Havet</h3>\n      <div class=\"arb-roots__sep\"></div>\n      <p class=\"arb-roots__body\">Det gränslösa. Våra produkter bär havets öppenhet — rymd utan att göra sig bred.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"arb-roots__cell\" style=\"background-image:url('https://arbetsro.searchboost.nu/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Hantverk.jpg')\">\n    <div class=\"arb-roots__inner\">\n      <h3 class=\"arb-roots__h3\">Hantverket</h3>\n      <div class=\"arb-roots__sep\"></div>\n      <p class=\"arb-roots__body\">Händer som format trä, metall och textil med tålamod. Välgjort är en tyst investering.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ========== SMK-band + CTA — sista raden ========== -->\n<section class=\"arb-bottom\">\n  <div class=\"arb-bottom__smk\">\n    <p class=\"arb-bottom__smk-eyebrow\">Arbetsro är en del av</p>\n    <h4>Smålands Kontorsmöbler</h4>\n    <p>Etablerad leverantör till svenska företag och offentliga miljöer. Arbetsro är vår satsning på hemmakontoret — samma hantverk, samma garantier.</p>\n    <a href=\"https://smalandskontorsmobler.se\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Besök smalandskontorsmobler.se →</a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"arb-bottom__cta\">\n    <p class=\"arb-bottom__cta-eyebrow\">Börja här</p>\n    <h3>Skapa din arbetsro</h3>\n    <p>Du behöver inte bygga om hela kontoret. Börja med ett bord. En stol. En lampa.</p>\n    <a class=\"btn\" href=\"/butik/\">Se sortimentet →</a>\n    <p class=\"micro\">Fri frakt över 1 000 kr · 30 dagars öppet köp · Baserad i Småland</p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- /wp:html -->",
  "excerpt": "<p>Direktören 2 990 kr Utforska → — Vår filosofi — Arbetsro är inte ett ställe.Det är ett tillstånd. En välgjord arbetsplats förändrar hur du tänker, hur du mår och vad du åstadkommer. Marseille 2 490 kr Ergo Höj-/sänk 3 234 kr Skjutdörrskåp 5 394 kr Mood Wall 1 890 kr Kongress fällbord 1 739 kr [&#8230;]\n",
